-- Harmony Gold Says Worker Killed in Fatal Accident at Its Kusasalethu Mine
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-10-21T10:17:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/harmony-gold-says-worker-killed-in-fatal-accident-at-its-kusasalethu-mine.html
Harmony Gold Mining Ltd. said a
worker was killed in a fatal accident at its Kusasalethu mine.  Hoisting operations at the mine have been temporarily
stopped, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
